and launch of the space vehicles. This constellation will be integrated into, and complementary, to the SDN-B creating a new
mission enclave. In addition to supporting the SBI program, the Space Data Network - Space Link will augment existing Space
Data Network - Backbone users.

FY 2026 Plans:
2026 efforts initiated within the mandatory Golden Dome for America account.
FY 2027 Plans:
Funds support the acceleration of the build-out of the Space Data Network to support the communication needs of the Space-
Based Interceptor missile defense system.
