Management Headquarters - STARCOM (1209158SF); Mgt Headquarters - Space (Admin) (1205498SF); Operational Headquarters - Space (1203925SF); Permanent
Change of Station Travel (0808731F); Service Support to OSW (0901503SF); Service Support to SDA - MHA (1201198SF); Space & Missile Systems Center - MHA
(1206398SF); Space Planning and Operations Support (1201000SF); Space Security and Defense Program (1206730SF); Space Warfighting Analysis (1203622SF);
Svc Spt to The Joint Staff (0901507SF)

