the GMTI system and forces to the Combatant Commands under Title 10 authority to enable kill chain closure and battle management functions. Additional details are
available at a higher classification level.

 The FY 2024 budget for GMTI was transferred from USAF to USSF in the FY 2024 Defense Appropriations Act.




