C. Accomplishments/Planned Programs ($ in Millions)                                                                           FY 2025      FY 2026       FY 2027
Title: WGS - BOOM Modernization                                                                                                   0.000       19.296         0.000
Description: WGS-BOOM Modernization encompasses three development efforts to improve the beam management panning
ability for WGS-11 & 12 missions utilizing the GSCCE, Common Network Planning (CNPS) and Power Control and Management

C. Accomplishments/Planned Programs ($ in Millions)                                                                                      FY 2025    FY 2026       FY 2027
Subsystem (PCMS). GSCCE and CNPS are existing ground systems with Boeing that performs payload commanding and
mission planning at all five of the Wideband SATCOM Operations Centers (WSOCs). PCMS is a system in development which
will improve the ability to rapidly plan WGS-11 & 12 missions. PCMS will establish machine-to-machine connection to terminals
to provide automated RF configuration management when problems are indicated and rapid restoral of services to begin before
operators identify a discrepancy. WGS-BOOM Modernization development upgrade will reduce commanding/commit time due to
increased commanding pace as a result of additional users/beams on WGS-11 & 12. This will result in the ability to rapidly plan
WGS-11 & 12 missions.

FY 2026 Plans:
Continue to build upon previous BOOM-PCMS development effort. PCMS will be fully deployed across the globe to provide
superior situational awareness of user resource usage and automated configuration capability to restore users. Activities may
include, but are not limited to program office support, studies, technical analysis, experimentation, risk reduction, prototyping, and
activities that may leverage commercial, U.S. Government partnership, and international opportunities to respond to existing and
emerging adversarial threats with speed and agility.
FY 2027 Plans:
NA
FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
Decrease due to completion of a one time add in FY26 to address minimum viable WGS ground enhancement BOOM
Modernization.
