Title: ECP                                                                                                                           1.369       0.000          0.000
Description: Energetic Charged Particles (ECP) will support the SBEM Weather Gap 11 and address the Secretary of the Air
Force (SECAF) policy which directed each Space Force Satellite Office to plan for ECP sensors on all pre-Milestone B satellite
acquisitions. To support this requirement, the ECP sensor will be integrated on the WSF-M satellites and include software
development, testing, and on-orbit support for the ECP sensor.

FY 2026 Plans:
The build and integration of the ECP sensor was finished in September 2025. No additional funding specific to ECP is necessary.
