D. Acquisition Strategy
The acquisition strategy for WSF is based on validated SBEM AoA results from FY 2014 and subsequent acquisition strategy development activities that were conducted
in FY 2015. The WSF acquisition strategy focuses on streamlined acquisition processes for providing materiel solutions to OSVW, TCI & LEO ECP, as validated by the
JROC; deliver microwave sensing solution to address DoW needs for OSVW and TCI capabilities and deliver space environment sensing solution to address LEO ECP
capabilities for on-orbit attributions and support of anomaly resolutions.

