FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY 2026 funds increased to resolve delays in NSA Crypto certification. NSA process delays and changes to respond to new
threat assessments is the single most critical factor in delaying fielding of new radios and capabilities. Additional resources are
already proving beneficial in assisting industry in leveraging the CDL CCM design to meet certification requirements. We will
extend that effort.
